---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="History | T2H3">
<section class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-10">
  <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-[2rem] border border-red-700/40 bg-black shadow-2xl">
    <div class="bg-[url('/images/dark-banner.jpg')] bg-cover bg-center">
      <div class="bg-black/75 p-10">
        <p class="text-sm font-black uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-teal-300">History</p>
        <h1 class="mt-3 text-5xl font-black text-white">True Trail Hash House Harriers</h1>
        <p class="mt-5 max-w-3xl text-zinc-300">
          Every kennel has a story. This page records the history of True Trail,
          memorable trails, legendary circles, milestone runs and the people who
          helped shape the kennel.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-8 grid gap-6">
    <article class="rounded-2xl border border-red-600/20 bg-zinc-900 p-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-red-500">The Beginning</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-zinc-300">
        Add the story of how T2H3 was founded, the first trail, and the vision
        behind the kennel.
      </p>
    </article>

    <article class="rounded-2xl border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-900 p-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-white">Milestones</h2>
      <ul class="mt-4 list-disc space-y-2 pl-6 text-zinc-300">
        <li>First Trail</li>
        <li>100th Trail</li>
        <li>200th Trail</li>
        <li>Special Events & Interhashes</li>
      </ul>
    </article>

    <article class="rounded-2xl border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-900 p-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-white">Traditions</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-zinc-300">
        At True Trail we believe the trail is meant to be followed. Checks,
        false trails and clever hare work are part of the adventure. Earn the
        finish, enjoy the circle, and help keep the traditions alive.
      </p>
    </article>

    <article class="rounded-2xl border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-900 p-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-white">Photo Timeline</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-zinc-400">
        Future enhancement: add historical photos and memorable moments from the
        kennel.
      </p>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>
</BaseLayout>
